name: Starry Nomads of the Evening Bog
description: Hailing from the Bogs of the <Anuran Countryside>, the Starry Nomads of the Evening Bog are known for their prowess with nearly any form of arms. Now armed with knowledge of the stars, moons, and tides, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
